Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对比这两家公司的话，虽然差距不大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但考虑到交货期等方面，我认为松岛商事更稳定一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,emmm不过B区块的利润率差得挺多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，部长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我漏看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上重新算一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田，你最近低级失误很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,核对的时候仔细点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，上周项目的反馈已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,负责人是足立吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个数字的依据在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,确实……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你大概是直接从下面的数字拉过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但计算对不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，你的失误会让公司损失多少信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在还在估算阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要说那么重吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你上周不也犯了同样的错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,平时就该保证数字准确无误，这是基本常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，吉冈，差不多……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个，明天会议前把这些改好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重新提交
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她真的好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明明长得那么漂亮，性格也太强势了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在公司里大概是被她骂得最惨的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不知道怎么跟她相处，总之太严了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过她肯定很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看那屁股，不是绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她有没有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,确实应该挺受欢迎的，但这性格真让人吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，部长，结果怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，虽说花了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次对方决定和我们签约了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这也全靠大家的努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是吉冈，作为主任非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,毫不夸张地说，这都是你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢部长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不不，吉冈，该说谢谢的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样，之后要不要办个庆祝会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去居酒屋可能来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司里干一杯怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就吉冈和足立吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能麻烦你们两个去准备一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，买点啤酒和简单的下酒菜就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，点些披萨和寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不用加班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,下班前把手头的工作好好做完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先去忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,部长照旧喝嗨棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,西中喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,披萨和寿司我来点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,足立，麻烦你去便利店和超市采购
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为要吃披萨，再买瓶便宜的红酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,红酒，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨棒和啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啤酒有指定品牌吗？还有红酒要白的还是红的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事不能自己想想吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啤酒什么牌子都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但这种场合可别买发泡酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，配披萨当然要白葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,公司里没有纸杯，你去车站前买些回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄酒和纸杯，好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你好歹也算个社会人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好歹自己动点脑子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,纸杯去百元店买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你5点前搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，为了庆祝新合约，干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家喝得挺多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈，你酒量很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头都打结了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好晕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该收拾一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,腿软了，起不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的……\N喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,起不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快来帮我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拉我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉我一把啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拉你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拉你起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拉你吗……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等下，等下……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就拉你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈的屁股有点……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢屁股的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都很中意吉冈前辈的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁股很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，不能再得寸进尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈，你这穿的什么内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你平时都穿这种的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得超赞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这形状也太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了我屁股很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再来，再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来，把腿伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢被人摸屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不自觉就动了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你扭来扭去的样子真的超色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里吗？喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再来点……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，直接摸不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,隔着丝袜摸就可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是那个意思……\N那就没关系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉简直好到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等等……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,皮肤好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等等……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你抖得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那里……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等下\N手感真的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,超级喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看你的正面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来，把腿抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,用手按住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，都被看光了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说你其实不讨厌被摸屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是，不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你被摸屁股时的样子超级可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股，能让我把脸埋进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是把脸埋进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就靠一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把头靠在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这么客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的屁股实在太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来，轮到吉冈前辈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让我来报答你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看你的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我让你舒服一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你用嘴帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还能看到你的屁股，太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想好好看看你的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能别一直盯着看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了，太会舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么舔得这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来换我来伺候你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，我可没说可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.30,0:24:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.28,0:24:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.60,0:24:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,变得超硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.84,0:25:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.30,0:25:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都舔成那样了，事到如今还有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了，这屁股……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.20,0:25:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,扭着屁股会越来越舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.62,0:26:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你的腰扭得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,扭得超厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.78,0:27:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.70,0:27:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,腰都浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.24,0:27:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.30,0:27:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别看了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.72,0:27:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这实在受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.72,0:27:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.77,0:28:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.31,0:28:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.74,0:29:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.82,0:30:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来从后面来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.08,0:30:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.08,0:30:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.66,0:30:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.75,0:30:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.64,0:30:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.26,0:31:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.10,0:31:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.59,0:31:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.92,0:31:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.75,0:31:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.30,0:31:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.82,0:31:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.46,0:32:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.72,0:32:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放得进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.23,0:32:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自己放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.06,0:33:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.58,0:33:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点动才行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.34,0:34:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.96,0:34:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就看不到你的屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.88,0:34:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.75,0:34:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.24,0:34:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.68,0:34:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.59,0:34:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.36,0:34:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再上来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.54,0:34:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样把屁股放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对，慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.14,0:35:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看慢慢进出的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.02,0:36:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.09,0:36:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来换我动
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.08,0:36:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把腿伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.34,0:36:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.62,0:36:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.06,0:38:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个要射在哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.55,0:38:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想射在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.16,0:38:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一般都是射里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.37,0:38:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.04,0:38:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就射在屁股上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把第14期的申请资料，还有安保资料都拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.79,0:39:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,西中，稍微过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.18,0:39:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,高桥在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.43,0:39:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我来处理，你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.57,0:39:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.48,0:39:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.54,0:40:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈，昨天的事……
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.35,0:40:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能把昨天的事忘掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.74,0:40:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟喝了点酒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.90,0:40:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.89,0:40:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等、都说了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.18,0:40:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.10,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天明明那么意乱情迷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.52,0:40:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,果然这屁股太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.05,0:40:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等下，不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,万一有人来了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.84,0:40:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那只要没人的地方就可以了？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.74,0:40:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.92,0:40:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.92,0:40:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.39,0:40:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要是像昨天那样叫那么大声的话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.86,0:40:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.41,0:40:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.44,0:41:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,万一有人来就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.41,0:41:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请不要出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.84,0:41:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.94,0:41:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.18,0:41:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.80,0:41:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等下，不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁股很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.78,0:41:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.24,0:41:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就继续，直到有人来为止
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.20,0:41:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.60,0:41:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛一直往我身上蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.30,0:42:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,腿都在打颤了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.36,0:42:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着西装裤的样子也好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.68,0:42:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.42,0:42:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,腰线勾勒得特别明显呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.94,0:42:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.44,0:42:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.20,0:42:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.24,0:42:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都说不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.60,0:42:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁股很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.18,0:43:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.68,0:43:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.07,0:43:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一直在发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.38,0:43:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了屁股很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.42,0:43:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.70,0:43:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,站着很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.16,0:43:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就干脆脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.96,0:43:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.17,0:43:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.66,0:43:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都会暴露，脱不脱都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.52,0:43:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.44,0:43:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.18,0:43:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.02,0:43:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.99,0:43:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.10,0:44:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.60,0:44:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你又穿这么骚的内衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.12,0:44:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢这种？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.91,0:44:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这种款式
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.70,0:44:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.98,0:44:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁股很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.50,0:44:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.03,0:44:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.94,0:44:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.72,0:44:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你这么喜欢被摸屁股的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.79,0:44:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来点更刺激的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.60,0:44:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.52,0:44:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.76,0:45:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.84,0:45:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,润滑液
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.00,0:45:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.14,0:45:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.10,0:45:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.84,0:45:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,润滑液怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.22,0:45:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿润滑液想干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.34,0:45:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.14,0:45:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.74,0:45:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你乱动的话会弄到衣服上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.32,0:45:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.18,0:45:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.38,0:45:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.56,0:45:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像超喜欢的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.50,0:46:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,超色的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.23,0:46:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司里做这种事……
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.22,0:46:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再多涂点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.06,0:46:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.52,0:46:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.26,0:46:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.10,0:46:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.62,0:47:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.52,0:47:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也滑溜溜的了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.28,0:47:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.45,0:47:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真的会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.12,0:47:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.16,0:47:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.57,0:47:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.45,0:48:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的，超舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.72,0:48:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.69,0:49:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.84,0:49:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都变成这副样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.28,0:49:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.20,0:49:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要弄下面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请夹紧屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.97,0:49:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,夹紧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.41,0:50:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超级滑
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.04,0:50:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.42,0:50:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,腿一直在抖
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.72,0:50:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.50,0:50:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.86,0:50:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.88,0:51:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.78,0:51:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底有多喜欢屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.34,0:51:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.18,0:51:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股撅起来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.56,0:52:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.18,0:52:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这种玩法我一直想试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.85,0:52:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.46,0:53:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.06,0:53:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.80,0:53:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再射在你屁股上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.48,0:54:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才超舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.36,0:54:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是想让我插进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.18,0:54:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.45,0:54:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.20,0:54:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那，我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.16,0:54:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那，这份资料我就放吉冈姐桌上了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.08,0:54:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.88,0:54:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,具体来说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.34,0:54:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要改变会员制型的雇佣环境
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.86,0:55:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为进行根本性的重新审视是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.30,0:55:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.13,0:55:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.27,0:55:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放到下次会议上讨论看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.72,0:55:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈，你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.40,0:55:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,着眼点确实不错
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.97,0:55:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但也得把技能重塑的事纳入考量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.70,0:55:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟足立经常犯低级失误
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.48,0:55:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你这也太严格了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.42,0:55:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎，吉冈前辈不也会失误嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.82,0:55:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,比如卡在沙发里什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.64,0:55:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，那个是……
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.71,0:55:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了，那就下次会议前
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.86,0:55:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再好好完善一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.23,0:55:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.79,0:55:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.36,0:56:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，那我们先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.02,0:56:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，说那种话要是被别人发现了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.30,0:56:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的啦，卡在沙发里什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.94,0:56:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁听了也不可能知道是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.46,0:56:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,总之在公司里别再提那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.82,0:56:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你特意把我留下来，难道是想和我独处？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.20,0:56:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.08,0:56:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.74,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.16,0:57:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.56,0:57:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，要叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.50,0:57:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦，要出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.10,0:57:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.34,0:57:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.16,0:57:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，这里是公司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.54,0:57:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是寂寞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.10,0:57:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.24,0:57:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没说过那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.14,0:57:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看看你的屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.74,0:58:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了这里是公司
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.56,0:58:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司里做，你不是更兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.56,0:58:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.50,0:58:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看看你的屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.00,0:58:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.80,0:58:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.14,0:58:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.84,0:58:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你讨厌这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.66,0:58:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,超色的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.11,0:58:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会叫出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.92,0:59:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,弄得太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.02,0:59:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那，轻一点比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.76,0:59:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.10,0:59:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去我真受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.24,0:59:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.52,0:59:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.78,1:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.32,1:01:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫得太大声了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.18,1:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.18,1:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.68,1:01:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我先把你的嘴堵上
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.60,1:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那，可以再用力一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.64,1:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对面没注意到吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.50,1:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没有
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.96,1:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.34,1:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明明湿得一塌糊涂嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.32,1:03:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好，吉冈姐
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.42,1:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐上来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.62,1:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在我身上
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.29,1:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.92,1:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.73,1:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.71,1:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，没事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.58,1:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会叫出声的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.96,1:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.64,1:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.02,1:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.64,1:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.64,1:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.44,1:05:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.04,1:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都很兴奋对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.20,1:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.22,1:06:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.72,1:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这条腿
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.30,1:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我舔了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.40,1:07:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是极品的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.80,1:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.34,1:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.38,1:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.34,1:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.10,1:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住别出声
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.12,1:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.06,1:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住别出声
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.72,1:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐一下，别出声
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.27,1:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.16,1:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是挺来劲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.80,1:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.98,1:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是想让我插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.20,1:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.40,1:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.04,1:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是自己动
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.45,1:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我来动
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.20,1:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.83,1:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种都受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.58,1:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那还是我来动比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.52,1:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都说受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.82,1:14:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.32,1:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.32,1:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.44,1:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.88,1:14:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.56,1:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.96,1:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,缓过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.36,1:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.30,1:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，明明刚才爽成那样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.96,1:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还能立马摆出这副正经脸
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.53,1:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这种话啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.44,1:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下一场会议要开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.12,1:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明明刚才还高潮了来着
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.74,1:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.75,1:15:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,坐哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.75,1:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不了，我在这边待会儿
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.38,1:15:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.83,1:15:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.96,1:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.78,1:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.34,1:16:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,忙完了？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.95,1:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,待会儿一起去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.92,1:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.04,1:16:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要跟女朋友去吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.11,1:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.48,1:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哎，吉冈前辈加班可真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.13,1:16:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微加会儿班
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.22,1:17:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.72,1:17:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你也快点弄完啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.01,1:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.76,1:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了，明天见
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.36,1:17:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也先下班了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.44,1:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等、等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.44,1:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你……你这就要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.05,1:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说，你是在等我？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.32,1:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没、并没有……那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.03,1:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.98,1:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说"请摸我的屁股"吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.92,1:18:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请摸我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.16,1:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,挺坦诚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.26,1:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那你得先把我伺候舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.14,1:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.42,1:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.90,1:19:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.02,1:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，你得先让我舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.76,1:19:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我摸你屁股对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.84,1:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先让我爽一爽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.54,1:19:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.90,1:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就这点本事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.66,1:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.04,1:19:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我舒服一点啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.54,1:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸得可真够色的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.42,1:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.86,1:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,给我舔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.12,1:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.96,1:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.70,1:21:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.62,1:22:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快继续
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.66,1:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.08,1:22:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.34,1:22:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,超兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.22,1:22:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈，你能不能一边自己弄着 一边让我摸
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.28,1:23:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一边自己弄？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.86,1:23:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一边弄弄这里
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.64,1:23:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,表情好诱人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.26,1:23:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一边自己弄一边被摸吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.42,1:24:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.48,1:24:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股撅起来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.06,1:24:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈，你今天的内衣也太骚了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.98,1:24:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特意精心挑的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.72,1:24:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,原来这里这么敏感
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.72,1:24:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明明才刚摸了几下而已
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.64,1:25:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤都陷进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.90,1:25:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.68,1:25:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.68,1:26:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全是吉冈前辈的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.70,1:26:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.90,1:27:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.75,1:27:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.72,1:27:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,转过来
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.86,1:27:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.72,1:28:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股摸着好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.06,1:28:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是喜欢屁股呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.96,1:28:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,光是玩屁股都快让我去了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.48,1:28:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.58,1:28:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,诶，你们还在啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.01,1:28:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,工作还没做完吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.73,1:28:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.63,1:28:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了有个案子必须结掉，打算现在赶一赶
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.50,1:29:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太可惜了，今天只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.24,1:29:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿……来我家吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.02,1:29:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去吉冈前辈家？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.66,1:29:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然被吉冈前辈主动邀请，看来你真是憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.36,1:29:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那种紧要关头被打断，怎么可能忍得住嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.92,1:29:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里就可以尽情释放了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.18,1:29:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也不用强忍着不出声了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.44,1:29:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.65,1:30:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.12,1:30:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,吉冈前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.08,1:31:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.56,1:31:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把我全都舔一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.86,1:32:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,全都？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.66,1:32:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.42,1:33:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我坐到你上面去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.08,1:33:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,用屁股蹭蹭我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.80,1:34:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.52,1:34:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.62,1:34:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.20,1:34:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.10,1:35:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我坐在你上面
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.16,1:35:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好好蹭蹭我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.77,1:35:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快摸摸我的屁股呀
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.42,1:35:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多摸摸我的屁股嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.16,1:35:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是很喜欢我的屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.40,1:36:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舔舔你的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.52,1:36:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股那里也在一抽一抽的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.25,1:36:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.26,1:37:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.70,1:37:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了，好舒服……
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.70,1:37:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行……
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.44,1:37:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.62,1:37:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.40,1:38:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.40,1:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.12,1:39:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来，把腿好好抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.28,1:39:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.40,1:39:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,硬得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.48,1:39:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.25,1:40:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,变得超硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.38,1:42:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去吧，好想一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.56,1:43:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好想一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.58,1:43:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.40,1:43:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你去得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.42,1:44:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了，去了！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.24,1:44:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.76,1:44:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,滑出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.94,1:44:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太舒服了嘛，没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.81,1:44:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我到上面去可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.64,1:44:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来看看
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.36,1:44:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.46,1:44:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那把屁股露给我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.36,1:45:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.62,1:45:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.42,1:45:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿得一塌糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.50,1:46:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叫声真好听
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.20,1:46:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.48,1:46:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头也伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.84,1:46:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,味道好香
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.21,1:46:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快点动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.04,1:46:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.70,1:47:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.18,1:47:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.42,1:47:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你去得可真快
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.71,1:48:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为太舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.84,1:48:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那我躺下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.56,1:48:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.62,1:48:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.84,1:48:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,里面已经湿得一塌糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.73,1:48:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.82,1:49:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来换你动
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.85,1:49:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好大
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.36,1:49:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来……
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.66,1:51:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能把屁股翘给我看吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.79,1:51:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情看我的屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.78,1:51:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.96,1:52:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太舒服了……
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.78,1:53:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.30,1:53:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,变得越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.54,1:54:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太舒服了……
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.98,1:55:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,必须让你顶到最里面才行
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.66,1:55:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就得顶到最里面
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.84,1:58:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛……你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.95,1:58:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，我也……
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.92,1:59:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我看看屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.96,1:59:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.60,2:00:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，你要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.84,2:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,继续待在这里也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.14,2:00:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我家住下吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.18,2:00:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.71,2:00:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,今天跟朋友约了喝酒，差不多该出门了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.33,2:00:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.36,2:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明还很期待的……
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.12,2:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.07,2:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你又想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.42,2:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,呐？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.84,2:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的有约了啦
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.63,2:00:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.92,2:01:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,又卡进去了，动不了了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.91,2:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我，快点 我动不了啦
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.60,2:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，快把我的屁股拔出来啊

